name: Pacsafe Prosafe 800 3-Dial Cable Lock
description: A three dial combo lock with a 10cm high tensile steel cable that is TSA approved so TSA (US) agents and HRSC (UK) officers can open and relock your bag using codes and secured tools – and leave your locks and bags undamaged.Lock is zinc alloy with a 10cm high-tensile steel cable.3-dial combo is resettable.
